
public class MapperAnagram {
	Open the input file
	Open a new output file
	For each word in the file 
	{
		assign a variable a = sort the characters in the word in ascending order
		add the (a, word) to the file
		Continue iterating
	}
	
	Sort the file;
}

Sample output
cat and the hat in tac

Before Sorting

act, cat
adn, and
eht, the
aht, hat
in, in
act, tac

After Sorting
act, cat
act, tac
adn, and
aht, hat
eht, the
in, in

